Content:
I'm looking to identify these motorcycles from a 1932 photo i have.

I can see one at the back that looks like it has a Ariel name on tank.
Looks like 1 of the bikes at front of photo has a M on the tank ?

Interesting photo of the riders with field Hockey sticks.
Photo was taken at South Chingford in London, England.

I'd like to tag other models in this pic, as people around the world visit HockeyGods, and we like to have correct info with our images.

Thank You for any help üôè
